Package org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.extensibility

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IQueryGroupProvider
    Provider interface for IQueryGroup instances with added method for requesting the set of FQNs for the query specifications in the group.
    IQuerySpecificationProvider
    Provider interface for IQuerySpecification instances with added method for requesting the FQN for the query specification.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PQueryExtensionFactory
    An extension factory to access PQuery instances from Query Specifications.
    QuerySpecificationRegistry Deprecated
    Use QuerySpecificationRegistry.getInstance() and read notes on deprecated methods for usage.
    SingletonExtensionFactory
    Factory to register a static singleton instance in an extension point.
    SingletonQueryGroupProvider
    Provider implementation for storing an existing query group instance.
    SingletonQuerySpecificationProvider
    Provider implementation for storing an existing query specification instance.
    ViatraQueryRuntimeConstants
    Utility class for Viatra Query runtime constants, such as extension point identifiers.
